fields.name: Cat Fleece Lined Winter Jacket Hoodie Cardigan Warm Puppy Clothes (Dark Blue-6 Inch)

Keeps your fur baby warm and dry while walking on cold. winter days or sleeping on chilly nights. Snap buttons under the chest for easy put on and take off. This style is for small breed dogs and cats only, please measure your pet before ordering.

fields.description: Suitable for all breeds of dogs. 100% natural ingredients. Contains farm fresh chicken liver. Antibiotic, hormone and preservative-free. Rich in Vitamin A and Iron

fields.name: Meat Up Adult Dry Dog Food, Chicken Flavour, 10 kg
fields.description: Omega 3 and 6 fatty acids for healthy skin and coat; Antioxidants for strong immune system. Probiotics in dry formula help maintain digestive health .Glucosamine for healthy joints and strong bones. Vitamins and minerals for complete and balanced nutrition

fields.name: Kong Classic Dog Toy (Large, Pack of 1)
fields.description: Revolutionary design makes toy bounce unpredictably in every direction. Hollow center can be stuffed with treats or peanut butter to give dogs an extra playtime challenge. Non-splintering, non-abrasive, does not get sharp when chewed. Made of thick, puncture-resistant rubber. Dome shape is hollow in the center; comes in large size; measures 4-1/2-inch height; 1-year limited warranty. fields.name: Self Cleaning Slicker Pet Grooming Brush | Pet Cleaning Tool Suitable for All Pets | Rectangular Shape
fields.description: Effortless Pet Grooming: Remove loose hair, shedding mats, tangles, and dirt from your pets with ease, ensuring a clean and healthy coat. Comfortable & Pet-Friendly: Designed with your pet's comfort in mind, this grooming tool is gentle on the skin, making it a pleasant experience for your furry friend. Ergonomic Design: The brush's ergonomic design ensures a comfortable grip, making it easy for you to groom your pet without strain or discomfort. Prevents Future Fur Loss: Regular use of this grooming tool helps prevent future pet fur loss, keeping your pet's coat in optimal condition and reducing the likelihood of excessive shedding.

fields.name: PAWPOURRI Ultra Soft Grey Bolster Pet Bed for Medium to Large Dogs, Cozy Cuddler, Polyfibre Filling
fields.description:
EASY TO USE - Our pawpourri beds are designed in a way where your pet can easily step in and out of the bed. This is keeping in mind common ailments and the general anatomy of your dog/pet such as artheritis, weak joins, short limbs etc.
DESIGN - these beds also have a bolster border which makes the bed more secure for your pet and poses as a neck rest making it more comfortable for them to sleep on. They are also light in weight and have a plush finish
PREMIUM QUALITY- Right from the look & feel to the actual filling material of the bed, we use eco-friendly and premium quality of fabrics and polyfills. This keeps your pooch comfortable while maintaining a modern aesthetic. This cuddler in particular has soft polyfill providing optimal comfort to your furry friend

fields.name: Outward Hound Fun Feeder Dog Bowl Slow Feeder Stop Bloat for Dogs
fields.description: Provides fun healthy eating. Helps prevent bloat, regurgitation and canine obesity. Made with food-safe ABS plastic. Features non-slip base to hold bowl in place. Holds up to 4 cups of dry dog food
